00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,360
<font color="yellow">No way, not this early.</font>

36
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:23,090
<font color="yellow">We should never doubt.</font>

37
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:33,360
<font color="yellow">- Is she not picking up?
- Is she not?</font>

