56
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:14,520
<font color="yellow">Forget about it.</font>

57
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:17,920
<font color="yellow">No, I don't know where she is.</font>

58
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:20,590
