69
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:53,990
<font color="yellow">Don't get it. Don't pick it up.</font>

70
00:03:57,390 --> 00:03:58,420
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

71
00:03:58,420 --> 00:04:00,020
