75
00:04:06,050 --> 00:04:07,950
<font color="yellow">She's done with you.</font>

76
00:04:09,050 --> 00:04:11,360
<font color="yellow">She's taking her revenge.</font>

77
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,390
<font color="yellow">She must be fine now if she has the energy to talk.</font>

78
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,420
<font color="yellow">Mum, I'm going to work.</font>

79
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:19,490
<font color="yellow">You're done for.</font>

80
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,890
<font color="yellow">How does it feel?</font>

81
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,490
<font color="yellow">How does it feel to be left alone?</font>

82
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:28,390
