86
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:42,340
<font color="yellow">She must have gone around town complaining about the work.</font>

87
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,890
<font color="yellow">What a whiner.</font>

88
00:04:44,550 --> 00:04:47,490
<font color="yellow">If she doesn't want to cook, she shouldn't have been a woman.</font>

89
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,160
<font color="yellow">Anyway, I was a good son...</font>

90
00:04:51,990 --> 00:04:54,090
