91
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,950
<font color="yellow">Soo Young?</font>

92
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,790
<font color="yellow">Did your mum come to your place to clean?</font>

93
00:05:04,550 --> 00:05:05,690
<font color="yellow">Let me talk to her if she's there.</font>

94
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:07,600
<font color="yellow">He didn't believe you?</font>

95
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:10,450
<font color="yellow">No. He only screamed more.</font>

96
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:16,220
<font color="yellow">(Professor Park)</font>

97
00:05:18,290 --> 00:05:20,120
<font color="yellow">I'll kill you all.</font>

98
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:24,720
<font color="yellow">Who? The professors that left you out yesterday?</font>

99
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,790
<font color="yellow">I'll take my revenge.</font>

100
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:30,150
<font color="yellow">Mum, go home.</font>

101
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,070
<font color="yellow">Wan, you should go, too.</font>

102
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,820
<font color="yellow">My nephews are coming.</font>

103
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:36,850
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam, that's wrong.</font>

104
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,650
<font color="yellow">Just don't see them any more.</font>

105
00:05:41,690 --> 00:05:43,720
<font color="yellow">Don't bother taking revenge.</font>

106
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:46,920
<font color="yellow">You'd have to see them again to take a revenge.</font>

107
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:50,250
<font color="yellow">You're too nice. They'll be able to fool you again.</font>

108
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:52,590
<font color="yellow">Listen to me. Okay?</font>

109
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:54,090
<font color="yellow">Be quiet.</font>

110
