113
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:20,750
<font color="yellow">I heard. Her name is Jacqueline, right?</font>

114
00:06:21,450 --> 00:06:23,090
<font color="yellow">What if she doesn't...</font>

115
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,920
<font color="yellow">like us two old people?</font>

116
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:30,950
<font color="yellow">Grandpa doesn't talk, so what's there to hate?</font>

117
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:32,750
<font color="yellow">Also, you're a charming lady.</font>

118
00:06:33,650 --> 00:06:35,190
<font color="yellow">You can make her like you.</font>

119
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,290
<font color="yellow">How?</font>

120
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:44,950
<font color="yellow">Give her money.</font>

121
00:06:46,290 --> 00:06:47,390
<font color="yellow">By getting a loan?</font>

122
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,550
<font color="yellow">Whatever you can afford.</font>

123
00:06:48,990 --> 00:06:53,150
<font color="yellow">The debt will go to them afterwards. You shouldn't get a loan.</font>

124
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:56,890
<font color="yellow">Do we eat with them while giving her the money?</font>

125
00:06:56,890 --> 00:06:58,450
<font color="yellow">Wire the money to her.</font>

126
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:01,390
<font color="yellow">Decline if she asks you to go out and eat.</font>

127
00:07:02,090 --> 00:07:05,450
<font color="yellow">If she asks you again, decline again.</font>

128
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:07,420
<font color="yellow">She's only saying that.</font>

129
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:09,720
<font color="yellow">Should we not even show our faces to her?</font>

130
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,090
<font color="yellow">- What about talking?
- Don't talk.</font>

131
00:07:13,650 --> 00:07:15,140
<font color="yellow">Unless they ask you something first.</font>

132
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:16,250
<font color="yellow">I shouldn't say anything?</font>

133
00:07:16,690 --> 00:07:17,690
<font color="yellow">If you can help it.</font>

134
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:21,750
<font color="yellow">Should I just keep my mouth shut?</font>

135
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,950
<font color="yellow">Yes, if you can.</font>

136
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,890
<font color="yellow">Should I just die instead?</font>

137
00:07:28,650 --> 00:07:30,750
<font color="yellow">You little...</font>

138
00:07:31,650 --> 00:07:33,550
<font color="yellow">Grandma, I didn't mean...</font>

139
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,150
<font color="yellow">What does that have to do with dying?</font>

140
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:41,050
<font color="yellow">I was just talking about kids these days.</font>

141
00:07:41,050 --> 00:07:42,460
<font color="yellow">"Kids these days"?</font>

142
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:45,690
<font color="yellow">Then what about you? What about you?</font>

143
00:07:45,690 --> 00:07:49,020
<font color="yellow">What I'm saying is, the adults should...</font>

144
00:07:49,020 --> 00:07:51,190
<font color="yellow">You're a mean wench!</font>

145
00:07:52,650 --> 00:07:54,490
<font color="yellow">Jacques will hate you.</font>

146
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:59,290
<font color="yellow">Be understanding.</font>

147
00:08:00,650 --> 00:08:02,820
<font color="yellow">Be understanding</font>

148
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:05,090
<font color="yellow">I have to write about them</font>

149
00:08:05,690 --> 00:08:07,590
<font color="yellow">Let's be understanding</font>

150
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:12,090
<font color="yellow">I'm digging my own grave, aren't I?</font>

151
00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:25,890
<font color="yellow">Yes, Soo Young.</font>

152
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:28,690
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja, where's my mum?</font>

153
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:30,580
<font color="yellow">She's not home.</font>

154
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:33,260
<font color="yellow">She ran away from your dad and left home.</font>

155
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:34,950
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

156
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:42,850
<font color="yellow">Seok Gyun is going crazy and this is Soo Young.</font>

157
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:46,190
<font color="yellow">What? Tell her I'll call back.</font>

158
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:50,550
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja.</font>

159
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:53,820
<font color="yellow">What do you mean she ran away from home?</font>

160
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:08,020
<font color="yellow">Here's your pillow.</font>

161
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,790
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

162
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:13,090
<font color="yellow">Sleep tight.</font>

163
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,590
<font color="yellow">(Ho Young)</font>

164
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:34,050
<font color="yellow">- I'm sorry.
- I'm sorry.</font>

165
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:36,950
<font color="yellow">How much?</font>

166
00:09:38,190 --> 00:09:39,530
<font color="yellow">I'm really sorry.</font>

167
00:09:39,530 --> 00:09:41,290
<font color="yellow">I didn't know you'd be sick.</font>

168
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:43,140
<font color="yellow">We really won't go to karaoke any more.</font>

169
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:44,690
<font color="yellow">You can go.</font>

170
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,650
<font color="yellow">But you have to pick up your phone.</font>

171
00:09:48,890 --> 00:09:51,020
<font color="yellow">An old person can get sick at any moment.</font>

172
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:54,090
<font color="yellow">I won't give you the cafe. Get lost.</font>

173
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:57,260
<font color="yellow">Don't.</font>

174
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,590
<font color="yellow">- Aunt...
- Let go.</font>

175
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:17,420
<font color="yellow">You jerks.</font>

176
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,550
<font color="yellow">I'll kill you all.</font>

177
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:26,190
<font color="yellow">Seok Gyun.</font>

178
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:29,020
<font color="yellow">Will you lay out the spoons and chopsticks?</font>

179
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:30,850
