00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,120
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

181
00:10:42,050 --> 00:10:43,190
<font color="yellow">Get your rice.</font>

182
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:54,390
<font color="yellow">How does this work?</font>

183
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:57,120
<font color="yellow">Oh, I got it.</font>

184
00:11:01,350 --> 00:11:02,920
<font color="yellow">Do you eat red rice?</font>

185
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,620
<font color="yellow">We do, too.</font>

186
00:11:06,250 --> 00:11:08,120
<font color="yellow">Eat a lot of it. It's good for you.</font>

187
00:11:09,090 --> 00:11:10,090
<font color="yellow">Seok Gyun.</font>

188
00:11:10,690 --> 00:11:13,160
<font color="yellow">Go and beg for forgiveness.</font>

189
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:15,080
<font color="yellow">Ask her to come home.</font>

190
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,090
<font color="yellow">What for?</font>

191
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,690
<font color="yellow">She'll be back in three days.</font>

192
00:11:18,690 --> 00:11:22,720
<font color="yellow">She'll come back by the time I finish all the soup and rice.</font>

193
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,210
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam is right.</font>

194
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:26,320
<font color="yellow">If she really did want to leave me,</font>

195
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,620
<font color="yellow">why would she have cooked me food?</font>

196
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,250
<font color="yellow">It's because that's what she's like.</font>

