198
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:38,340
<font color="yellow">It's your last feast.</font>

199
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:40,340
<font color="yellow">"Eat the rice and soup,"</font>

200
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:42,850
<font color="yellow">"and stay away for the rest of my life."</font>

201
00:11:43,220 --> 00:11:44,420
<font color="yellow">That's what she means.</font>

202
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:46,280
<font color="yellow">She's that sweet.</font>

203
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:48,490
<font color="yellow">Where are the divorce papers then?</font>

204
