<font color="yellow">Aren't I right? I got you there.</font>

205
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:58,990
<font color="yellow">My wife will never,</font>

206
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:02,140
<font color="yellow">ever divorce me.</font>

207
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:04,700
<font color="yellow">We were married for half a century.</font>

208
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,320
<font color="yellow">You may think that...</font>

209
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,130
<font color="yellow">I'm a jerk, but I'm not.</font>

210
00:12:09,130 --> 00:12:11,550
<font color="yellow">I'm a great husband. I support us...</font>

211
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:14,690
<font color="yellow">and never had an affair.</font>

212
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:17,290
<font color="yellow">You did.</font>

213
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,790
<font color="yellow">Jeong A...</font>

214
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,720
<font color="yellow">rented a house.</font>

215
00:12:26,850 --> 00:12:28,180
<font color="yellow">That's for show.</font>

216
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:30,720
<font color="yellow">She wanted me to take her around the world,</font>

