00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:50,370
<font color="yellow">I can't hear things that don't make sense.</font>

435
00:26:50,870 --> 00:26:52,700
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

436
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:56,100
<font color="yellow">Read this later.</font>

437
00:26:56,770 --> 00:26:57,950
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

438
00:26:57,950 --> 00:26:59,040
<font color="yellow">You'll see.</font>

439
00:27:01,670 --> 00:27:02,940
<font color="yellow">(How to Be a Good Husband)</font>

440
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,500
<font color="yellow">Hurry up.</font>

441
00:27:06,670 --> 00:27:08,060
<font color="yellow">Don't rush me.</font>

442
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:10,000
<font color="yellow">We're both getting old. You're not that much older.</font>

443
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:12,570
<font color="yellow">Don't tell me what to do. It's annoying.</font>

444
00:27:12,570 --> 00:27:13,660
<font color="yellow">Sorry.</font>

445
00:27:13,660 --> 00:27:15,840
<font color="yellow">You must be annoyed because of me.</font>

446
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:18,270
<font color="yellow">Then tell Jeong A to come back.</font>

447
00:27:18,770 --> 00:27:21,640
<font color="yellow">Otherwise, you'll have to pick up after me.</font>

448
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:24,540
<font color="yellow">I'll call you every day. I'll call you 12 times a day.</font>

449
00:27:24,970 --> 00:27:26,510
<font color="yellow">- Seok Gyun.
- What?</font>

450
00:27:26,510 --> 00:27:29,710
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'll come back again to do your dishes?</font>

451
00:27:29,710 --> 00:27:32,870
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'd come here in between my shoots?</font>

452
00:27:32,870 --> 00:27:34,270
<font color="yellow">Don't you dare.</font>

453
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,440
<font color="yellow">Mark my words.</font>

454
00:27:35,970 --> 00:27:38,660
<font color="yellow">It'll be just once. Today and today only.</font>

455
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:40,210
<font color="yellow">I'll call you again.</font>

456
00:27:40,210 --> 00:27:42,000
<font color="yellow">We'll mark you as spam.</font>

457
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:44,040
<font color="yellow">What? Spam?</font>

458
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:45,770
<font color="yellow">This is wrong.</font>

459
00:27:45,770 --> 00:27:48,570
<font color="yellow">If it's uncomfortable, you should go and beg her. This is wrong.</font>

460
00:27:48,570 --> 00:27:49,960
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

461
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:52,350
<font color="yellow">You got her to do it, didn't you?</font>

462
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:54,370
<font color="yellow">You told an innocent, old lady to get a divorce!</font>

463
00:27:54,370 --> 00:27:56,070
<font color="yellow">What is it? Female rights?</font>

464
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:57,140
<font color="yellow">I did.</font>

465
00:27:58,070 --> 00:28:00,300
<font color="yellow">Hey, I'll wait outside.</font>

466
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:03,540
<font color="yellow">Yesterday, my appendix exploded. But today, my head will explode.</font>

467
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:05,360
<font color="yellow">Hey, Choong Nam!</font>

468
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:08,200
<font color="yellow">She found the house and you lent her the money, right?</font>

469
00:28:08,570 --> 00:28:09,600
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

470
00:28:13,540 --> 00:28:16,300
<font color="yellow">I tried to stop her. I told her not to do it.</font>

471
00:28:16,870 --> 00:28:19,770
<font color="yellow">I told her to keep serving you until the end...</font>

472
00:28:19,770 --> 00:28:21,870
<font color="yellow">since that's what she's done all her life.</font>

473
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:24,660
<font color="yellow">Are you on my side then?</font>

474
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,740
<font color="yellow">But I change my mind.</font>

475
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:28,440
<font color="yellow">I was too cruel to her.</font>

476
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:30,790
<font color="yellow">If you're being like this to me, she must have had it worse.</font>

477
00:28:30,790 --> 00:28:33,900
<font color="yellow">She should live the way she wants for whatever she has left.</font>

478
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:35,440
<font color="yellow">I'm glad this happened.</font>

479
00:28:35,770 --> 00:28:38,900
<font color="yellow">Also, if you need someone to do your housework,</font>

480
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,720
<font color="yellow">call your siblings.</font>

481
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:43,260
<font color="yellow">Call the ones you gave away all your money to...</font>

482
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:45,170
<font color="yellow">and tell them to work for you.</font>

483
00:28:45,170 --> 00:28:46,440
<font color="yellow">They're all men.</font>

484
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,500
<font color="yellow">I'm a woman! So what?</font>

485
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,840
<font color="yellow">Be quiet.</font>

486
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,940
<font color="yellow">If you're loud, I'll leave.</font>

487
00:28:54,370 --> 00:28:55,470
<font color="yellow">I won't do the dishes.</font>

488
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:01,110
<font color="yellow">Let me tell you this.</font>

489
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:02,290
<font color="yellow">Going to the same elementary school...</font>

490
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:04,100
<font color="yellow">doesn't mean we have legal ties, okay?</font>

491
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:06,550
<font color="yellow">We are legal strangers.</font>

492
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:09,070
<font color="yellow">I'm going to get her. She called.</font>

493
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:10,670
<font color="yellow">She told me to come over.</font>

494
00:29:10,670 --> 00:29:12,800
<font color="yellow">It's her final farewell, you idiot.</font>

495
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:15,100
<font color="yellow">Clean the room and the basin!</font>

496
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:37,270
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't be doing any housework.</font>

497
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:40,470
<font color="yellow">I'm repaying the debt for when he beat up...</font>

498
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:43,200
<font color="yellow">the kids who bullied me in school.</font>

499
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:47,970
<font color="yellow">I hate myself for remembering all that.</font>

500
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:51,040
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won. Right.</font>

501
00:29:51,870 --> 00:29:54,400
<font color="yellow">Help me get revenge.</font>

502
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:56,400
<font color="yellow">Who's the target?</font>

503
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:59,200
<font color="yellow">The professors who left me out.</font>

504
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:04,370
<font color="yellow">Let's do it. We're in a foul mood, so let's do something about it.</font>

505
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,300
<font color="yellow">Do you have a plan?</font>

506
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:09,400
<font color="yellow">I'm thinking of one.</font>

507
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:14,300
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

508
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:18,350
<font color="yellow">I passed the green gate. Where do you live?</font>

509
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:19,540
<font color="yellow">Look up.</font>

510
00:30:51,600 --> 00:30:53,200
<font color="yellow">I cared for my parents.</font>

511
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:55,140
<font color="yellow">What's wrong about that?</font>

512
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:58,840
<font color="yellow">What's so wrong about me giving money to my siblings?</font>

513
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:01,200
<font color="yellow">Tell me. Go on.</font>

514
00:31:02,570 --> 00:31:03,770
<font color="yellow">Nothing's wrong.</font>

515
00:31:04,170 --> 00:31:06,770
<font color="yellow">Just divorce me. Why move out?</font>

516
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:09,470
<font color="yellow">What? Are you too scared to get divorced?</font>

517
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:12,770
<font color="yellow">If this is what you want, let's get a divorce.</font>

518
00:31:34,870 --> 00:31:38,340
<font color="yellow">I signed the divorce papers. Sign it and hand it in.</font>

519
00:31:41,270 --> 00:31:42,270
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

520
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:44,140
<font color="yellow">Let's get divorced.</font>

521
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:47,320
<font color="yellow">But this house is mine.</font>

522
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:50,000
<font color="yellow">It's in your name, but it's mine.</font>

523
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,470
<font color="yellow">Do you want a lawsuit?</font>

524
00:31:51,470 --> 00:31:52,500
<font color="yellow">Are you scared?</font>

525
00:31:52,970 --> 00:31:54,100
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

526
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,700
<font color="yellow">Let's go to court.</font>

527
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:02,540
<font color="yellow">What did I do that's so wrong?</font>

528
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:05,980
<font color="yellow">My parents told me to look after my siblings...</font>

529
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:08,040
<font color="yellow">because it's my duty as the eldest.</font>

530
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:10,740
<font color="yellow">All I did was obey their last words.</font>

531
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:14,030
<font color="yellow">Is it terribly wrong for a son to do as he was told?</font>

532
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:17,660
<font color="yellow">When my parents scorned you for not having a son,</font>

533
00:32:17,660 --> 00:32:20,400
<font color="yellow">I left home instead of siding with them!</font>

534
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:23,600
<font color="yellow">I abandoned them like an old shoe for your sake!</font>

535
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:26,360
<font color="yellow">You did not abandon them. You moved next door...</font>

536
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:29,680
<font color="yellow">and I had to go over at dawn to cook and clean for them.</font>

537
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:32,460
<font color="yellow">They pulled out my hair whenever they had the chance.</font>

538
00:32:32,460 --> 00:32:35,180
<font color="yellow">Honey. You did not abandon them.</font>

539
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:37,570
<font color="yellow">Get your facts straight. You just moved out.</font>

540
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:41,190
<font color="yellow">Don't call me honey if you want a divorce.</font>

541
00:32:41,190 --> 00:32:44,110
<font color="yellow">You're right. What should I call you then?</font>

542
00:32:44,110 --> 00:32:46,640
<font color="yellow">Should I call you by your name like Hee Ja does?</font>

543
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:50,340
<font color="yellow">See you in court.</font>

544
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:56,000
<font color="yellow">It's a long walk down. Take care.</font>

545
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:03,350
<font color="yellow">What did I do that's so wrong?</font>

546
00:33:03,350 --> 00:33:04,700
<font color="yellow">Not take you around the world?</font>

547
00:33:05,170 --> 00:33:08,040
<font color="yellow">Is it so wrong that I want to save money?</font>

548
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:11,540
<font color="yellow">Don't make me repeat myself. You did nothing wrong.</font>

549
00:33:11,540 --> 00:33:14,040
<font color="yellow">My whole life, parents were my first priority...</font>

550
00:33:14,570 --> 00:33:16,740
<font color="yellow">and my siblings came second. Is that so wrong?</font>

551
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:21,240
<font color="yellow">If your siblings come after your parents,</font>

552
00:33:21,570 --> 00:33:23,600
<font color="yellow">then go live with them.</font>

553
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:28,530
<font color="yellow">Before my mum died, she told me to live a comfortable life.</font>

554
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:30,270
<font color="yellow">That's why I moved out.</font>

555
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:33,580
<font color="yellow">I could barely handle my own life, so I sent her to a care home.</font>

556
00:33:33,580 --> 00:33:35,800
<font color="yellow">And I ended up taking her to the beach where she died.</font>

557
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:39,640
<font color="yellow">But I will obey my mum's dying wish.</font>

558
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:42,570
<font color="yellow">I can be just a good a child, too!</font>

559
00:33:58,570 --> 00:34:00,870
<font color="yellow">You weren't that great a wife!</font>

560
00:34:12,370 --> 00:34:13,780
<font color="yellow">I will do it.</font>

561
00:34:13,780 --> 00:34:15,440
<font color="yellow">Stay in your seat.</font>

562
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,200
<font color="yellow">You're good at this.</font>

563
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:23,900
<font color="yellow">My wife taught me well.</font>

564
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:26,170
<font color="yellow">She was very strict...</font>

565
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:29,850
<font color="yellow">for the last three years of her life.</font>

566
00:34:29,850 --> 00:34:33,020
<font color="yellow">She did that so you could survive on your own without her.</font>

567
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:35,740
<font color="yellow">That's all done.</font>

568
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:37,880
<font color="yellow">Now, I need some vinegar.</font>

569
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:38,940
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

570
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:45,600
<font color="yellow">Who made this mess?</font>

571
00:34:46,570 --> 00:34:47,900
<font color="yellow">Use salt instead.</font>

572
00:34:49,700 --> 00:34:50,870
<font color="yellow">- Salt?
- Salt.</font>

573
00:34:51,870 --> 00:34:54,300
<font color="yellow">Yes. That will work, too.</font>

574
00:34:58,700 --> 00:34:59,940
<font color="yellow">(Secret Garden)</font>

575
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,370
<font color="yellow">Didn't I do well?</font>

576
00:35:10,370 --> 00:35:11,940
<font color="yellow">It's lovely.</font>

577
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:13,700
<font color="yellow">Good for you.</font>

578
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,520
<font color="yellow">It's a great way to kill time.</font>

579
00:35:15,520 --> 00:35:18,440
<font color="yellow">Yes. That's a problem for people our age.</font>

580
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:23,360
<font color="yellow">Oh, gosh. You did so very well.</font>

581
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,740
<font color="yellow">I did more.</font>

582
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:26,340
<font color="yellow">You're having fun.</font>

583
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,510
<font color="yellow">How did you get in?</font>

584
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:31,940
<font color="yellow">I walked in. I'm too old to scale the wall.</font>

585
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:32,970
<font color="yellow">Where's Yeong Won?</font>

586
00:35:32,970 --> 00:35:34,150
<font color="yellow">Parking the car.</font>

587
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,400
<font color="yellow">I'll bring some tea.</font>

588
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,400
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

589
00:35:39,010 --> 00:35:40,440
<font color="yellow">I meant to visit you,</font>

590
00:35:41,170 --> 00:35:44,030
<font color="yellow">but I couldn't because I crashed the car. Sorry.</font>

591
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:47,040
<font color="yellow">It's fine. Be nice to her instead.</font>

592
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:48,770
<font color="yellow">I'll kill you if you aren't.</font>

593
00:35:51,270 --> 00:35:53,320
<font color="yellow">What's wrong? Does your shoulder hurt?</font>

594
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:56,540
<font color="yellow">Yes. I guess I clung to the walking frame too hard.</font>

595
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:58,940
<font color="yellow">Let me massage your shoulders.</font>

596
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:03,140
<font color="yellow">I'll borrow him for a bit.</font>

597
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,870
<font color="yellow">Keep him.</font>

598
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:06,840
<font color="yellow">Can I keep you?</font>

599
00:36:08,570 --> 00:36:09,680
<font color="yellow">How does it feel?</font>

600
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:12,370
<font color="yellow">It hurts. Don't be so rough.</font>

601
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,610
<font color="yellow">Is that you, Gi Ja?</font>

602
00:36:14,610 --> 00:36:16,240
<font color="yellow">Why are you writing about me?</font>

603
00:36:16,240 --> 00:36:18,010
<font color="yellow">It's for a novel.</font>

604
00:36:18,010 --> 00:36:20,540
<font color="yellow">I'm busy, so listen to my story first.</font>

605
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:22,040
<font color="yellow">Let the eldest go first.</font>

606
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:24,540
<font color="yellow">- We're all busy people, come on.
- She's right.</font>

607
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:26,370
<font color="yellow">Will you all be quiet?</font>

608
00:36:26,370 --> 00:36:28,840
<font color="yellow">Wan's too confused to write.</font>

609
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:32,200
<font color="yellow">Why would she be confused? She understands us just fine.</font>

610
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:35,140
<font color="yellow">What will you write? I have to know.</font>

611
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:38,370
<font color="yellow">- What's wrong?
- What is it?</font>

612
00:36:38,370 --> 00:36:40,870
<font color="yellow">Wan, I'm very busy.</font>

613
00:36:40,870 --> 00:36:42,540
<font color="yellow">Let me go first.</font>

614
00:36:42,540 --> 00:36:45,670
<font color="yellow">The more you interrupt, the longer she needs. Let her talk.</font>

615
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:48,540
<font color="yellow">Hey. I mean, ladies.</font>

616
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:52,070
<font color="yellow">I'm interviewing you to write a book.</font>

617
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:54,640
<font color="yellow">I won't be writing about your sad lives.</font>

618
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:56,480
<font color="yellow">It's just a novel.</font>

619
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:58,340
<font color="yellow">- The concept is...
- What's a concept?</font>

620
00:36:58,340 --> 00:37:00,270
<font color="yellow">- What's that?
- It doesn't matter.</font>

621
00:37:00,270 --> 00:37:01,540
<font color="yellow">Why would she mention it then?</font>

622
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:03,100
<font color="yellow">- Go on.
- Talk.</font>

623
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,140
<font color="yellow">We're listening.</font>

624
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:10,740
<font color="yellow">My book will target the younger generations.</font>

625
00:37:10,740 --> 00:37:13,150
<font color="yellow">Will it not be about us, then?</font>

626
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:16,770
<font color="yellow">Young people aren't interested in old people...</font>

627
00:37:16,770 --> 00:37:18,440
<font color="yellow">whining about...</font>

628
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:21,540
<font color="yellow">how tough their lives were or how sad they felt.</font>

629
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:24,300
<font color="yellow">We get it. They don't care.</font>

630
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:28,270
<font color="yellow">You want us to answer your questions and not add anything else...</font>

631
00:37:28,270 --> 00:37:31,240
<font color="yellow">because there's no time for that, right?</font>

632
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:32,640
<font color="yellow">Bingo.</font>

633
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:35,040
<font color="yellow">But don't you want to know about your mum's love life?</font>

634
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:37,970
<font color="yellow">She's wouldn't know. She's not a mum.</font>

635
00:37:38,940 --> 00:37:40,770
<font color="yellow">What? I'm a virgin.</font>

636
00:37:40,770 --> 00:37:42,740
<font color="yellow">Let the childless be silent.</font>

637
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:47,640
<font color="yellow">So you are saying that you came up with...</font>

638
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:50,430
<font color="yellow">a theme or keyword for each of us.</font>

639
00:37:50,430 --> 00:37:53,930
<font color="yellow">I'm the actress who is the symbol of love.</font>

640
00:37:53,930 --> 00:37:56,320
<font color="yellow">I'm the friendly mum. I like that.</font>

641
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,390
<font color="yellow">Don't forget to mention our fights.</font>

642
00:37:58,390 --> 00:38:00,300
<font color="yellow">Don't be hesitant to write in detail.</font>

643
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:02,600
<font color="yellow">- You even threw a vase.
- A vase?</font>

644
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:03,940
