00:47:05,300 --> 00:47:09,160
<font color="yellow">Then comes Grandma Sook Hyun and her cruel revenge.</font>

853
00:47:09,160 --> 00:47:10,170
<font color="yellow">She's Choong Nam's mother.</font>

854
00:47:10,940 --> 00:47:13,990
<font color="yellow">Is it really in the ten thousands?</font>

855
00:47:13,990 --> 00:47:15,000
<font color="yellow">I think so.</font>

856
00:47:15,470 --> 00:47:17,390
<font color="yellow">My grandma is pretty bad, too.</font>

857
00:47:17,390 --> 00:47:20,650
<font color="yellow">Is she really keeping this up just to take revenge on her husband?</font>

858
00:47:20,650 --> 00:47:21,820
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

859
00:47:21,820 --> 00:47:25,740
<font color="yellow">Don't we need at least a page of romance?</font>

860
00:47:25,740 --> 00:47:28,490
<font color="yellow">We have it. We have just that.</font>

861
00:47:28,490 --> 00:47:30,940
<font color="yellow">The lawyer Seong Jae and the odd Hee Ja.</font>

862
00:47:32,540 --> 00:47:35,300
<font color="yellow">No. Yeong Won is better suited for romance.</font>

863
00:47:35,970 --> 00:47:37,460
<font color="yellow">Oh, you mean the actress?</font>

864
00:47:37,460 --> 00:47:38,470
<font color="yellow">She's the actress, right?</font>

865
00:47:38,940 --> 00:47:40,830
<font color="yellow">- This is amazing.
- It's so good.</font>

866
00:47:40,830 --> 00:47:42,220
<font color="yellow">I told you it's amazing.</font>

867
00:47:42,220 --> 00:47:43,670
<font color="yellow">It's so cool.</font>

868
00:47:49,870 --> 00:47:50,870
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

869
00:47:51,870 --> 00:47:53,910
<font color="yellow">Come on, dance with him once.</font>

870
00:47:53,910 --> 00:47:56,090
<font color="yellow">He's been doing this for three days.</font>

871
00:47:56,090 --> 00:47:57,940
<font color="yellow">Be generous, please?</font>

872
00:47:57,940 --> 00:48:00,540
<font color="yellow">- Come on.
- I don't want to.</font>

873
00:48:00,540 --> 00:48:03,030
<font color="yellow">Goodness. You're going to be blessed.</font>

874
00:48:03,030 --> 00:48:04,100
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

875
00:48:09,270 --> 00:48:10,270
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

876
00:48:11,140 --> 00:48:12,140
<font color="yellow">Rice?</font>

877
00:48:12,470 --> 00:48:13,740
<font color="yellow">It's in the cooker.</font>

878
00:48:14,940 --> 00:48:16,210
<font color="yellow">Money?</font>

879
00:48:16,210 --> 00:48:17,270
<font color="yellow">I don't have any!</font>

880
00:48:23,840 --> 00:48:25,360
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, what do you think...</font>

881
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:28,070
<font color="yellow">I decided to write the stories of the elders...</font>

882
00:48:28,070 --> 00:48:30,700
<font color="yellow">as they are without sugar-coating them.</font>

883
00:48:32,100 --> 00:48:33,370
<font color="yellow">If this tiring...</font>

884
00:48:33,700 --> 00:48:35,400
<font color="yellow">and lousy life...</font>

885
00:48:35,840 --> 00:48:37,970
<font color="yellow">is really what life is like,</font>

886
00:48:38,770 --> 00:48:40,300
<font color="yellow">then there's nothing I can do.</font>

887
00:48:41,470 --> 00:48:44,240
<font color="yellow">I decided to only write what's true.</font>

888
00:48:45,770 --> 00:48:48,270
<font color="yellow">They're the protagonists of their lives.</font>

889
00:48:48,700 --> 00:48:50,670
<font color="yellow">So they have the right to choose.</font>

890
00:49:11,200 --> 00:49:12,240
<font color="yellow">Oh dear.</font>

891
00:49:21,500 --> 00:49:22,640
<font color="yellow">It's so hot.</font>

892
00:49:35,800 --> 00:49:37,740
<font color="yellow">Wan. Are you asleep?</font>

893
00:49:38,400 --> 00:49:39,400
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

894
00:49:40,300 --> 00:49:41,980
<font color="yellow">I made up my mind.</font>

895
00:49:41,980 --> 00:49:44,140
<font color="yellow">Can't you still change it?</font>

896
00:49:44,840 --> 00:49:49,080
<font color="yellow">I make rosaries every evening and I'm afraid that will...</font>

897
00:49:49,080 --> 00:49:51,440
<font color="yellow">upset the kids and make them worry.</font>

898
00:49:51,900 --> 00:49:54,670
<font color="yellow">Can't you say I'm doing it...</font>

899
00:49:54,670 --> 00:49:57,740
<font color="yellow">for the community and not out of loneliness?</font>

900
00:49:58,700 --> 00:50:00,670
<font color="yellow">I'm a mother...</font>

901
00:50:01,470 --> 00:50:04,830
<font color="yellow">so I shouldn't do anything to cause them concern.</font>

902
00:50:04,830 --> 00:50:05,840
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja.</font>

903
00:50:06,700 --> 00:50:10,480
<font color="yellow">Your life is already all about caring for others.</font>

904
00:50:10,480 --> 00:50:13,170
<font color="yellow">You did enough. They have to know...</font>

905
00:50:13,600 --> 00:50:15,500
<font color="yellow">about your long, lonely nights.</font>

906
00:50:17,740 --> 00:50:19,700
<font color="yellow">Hang up and go to bed.</font>

907
00:50:20,140 --> 00:50:21,140
<font color="yellow">Be strong.</font>

908
00:50:30,600 --> 00:50:31,600
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

909
00:50:33,400 --> 00:50:35,280
<font color="yellow">What I said earlier today?</font>

910
00:50:35,280 --> 00:50:37,370
<font color="yellow">I didn't move out to get revenge.</font>

911
00:50:38,670 --> 00:50:40,940
<font color="yellow">You said that's what it looks like.</font>

912
00:50:41,700 --> 00:50:44,200
<font color="yellow">I'm having some dark beer and now I feel...</font>

913
00:50:44,200 --> 00:50:45,770
<font color="yellow">all sad and bitter.</font>

914
00:50:47,470 --> 00:50:50,400
<font color="yellow">I want to leave my girls out because it'll cause pain...</font>

915
00:50:50,400 --> 00:50:51,840
<font color="yellow">for them, not for me.</font>

916
00:50:53,370 --> 00:50:55,100
<font color="yellow">Why else would I move out...</font>

917
00:50:55,100 --> 00:50:56,100
<font color="yellow">if it's not for revenge?</font>

918
00:50:56,870 --> 00:51:00,100
<font color="yellow">It really isn't about getting revenge at all.</font>

919
00:51:01,670 --> 00:51:03,000
<font color="yellow">It's just...</font>

920
00:51:04,570 --> 00:51:09,470
<font color="yellow">I just want to be able to have a beer whenever I want to.</font>

921
00:51:10,870 --> 00:51:12,000
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

922
00:51:12,900 --> 00:51:15,190
<font color="yellow">You didn't move out to get revenge.</font>

923
00:51:15,190 --> 00:51:18,000
<font color="yellow">You slaved away for your in-laws, husband and daughters.</font>

924
00:51:18,000 --> 00:51:22,020
<font color="yellow">And you moved out to enjoy a beer. It's not about revenge at all.</font>

925
00:51:22,020 --> 00:51:25,600
<font color="yellow">I was too harsh when we talked today.</font>

926
00:51:26,870 --> 00:51:28,040
<font color="yellow">I'm too young.</font>

927
00:51:29,740 --> 00:51:30,740
<font color="yellow">She's right.</font>

928
00:51:31,100 --> 00:51:33,070
<font color="yellow">Revenge isn't part of her life.</font>

929
00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:37,400
<font color="yellow">She lived for her in-laws, husband and daughters.</font>

930
00:51:37,900 --> 00:51:41,300
<font color="yellow">And now, she finally got to enjoy a beer.</font>

931
00:51:41,300 --> 00:51:42,970
<font color="yellow">How could that be revenge?</font>

932
00:51:43,570 --> 00:51:45,840
<font color="yellow">It's the furthest thing from it.</font>

933
00:51:54,700 --> 00:51:56,840
<font color="yellow">Thank you very much.</font>

934
00:52:05,740 --> 00:52:09,370
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam, isn't this one of my works?</font>

935
00:52:10,100 --> 00:52:13,170
<font color="yellow">It's perfect as a fruit bowl.</font>

936
00:52:13,740 --> 00:52:15,870
<font color="yellow">Let's see how good a fruit salad...</font>

937
00:52:15,870 --> 00:52:17,840
<font color="yellow">in a 2,000-dollar bowl tastes like.</font>

938
00:52:26,470 --> 00:52:29,000
<font color="yellow">Sorry. This one cost 300 dollars.</font>

939
00:52:29,000 --> 00:52:32,000
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, it's fine. Throw the pieces away.</font>

940
00:52:32,000 --> 00:52:35,880
<font color="yellow">Over there is another one that costs 3,000 dollars.</font>

941
00:52:35,880 --> 00:52:38,140
<font color="yellow">It's the white one. Use that instead.</font>

942
00:52:39,670 --> 00:52:40,670
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

943
00:52:41,370 --> 00:52:44,270
<font color="yellow">That piece meant a lot to me.</font>

944
00:52:46,740 --> 00:52:47,740
<font color="yellow">Aunt.</font>

945
00:52:49,870 --> 00:52:53,400
<font color="yellow">These are Professor Yang's. You wished you could afford one.</font>

946
00:52:53,400 --> 00:52:56,470
<font color="yellow">I'm selling them at half price today.</font>

947
00:52:56,470 --> 00:52:57,500
<font color="yellow">Are you interested?</font>

948
00:52:57,500 --> 00:52:58,500
<font color="yellow">How could you...</font>

949
00:52:58,870 --> 00:52:59,870
<font color="yellow">even think of...</font>

950
00:53:00,370 --> 00:53:02,740
<font color="yellow">selling them at such a cheap price?</font>

951
00:53:04,100 --> 00:53:07,180
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam, I put my soul into my work.</font>

952
00:53:07,180 --> 00:53:08,900
<font color="yellow">How could you use it as a fruit bowl?</font>

953
00:53:08,900 --> 00:53:11,400
<font color="yellow">And I don't have cash. I only have a credit card.</font>

954
00:53:11,400 --> 00:53:14,070
<font color="yellow">You can pay me over 12 months. Do you want them?</font>

955
00:53:14,900 --> 00:53:15,900
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

956
00:53:16,800 --> 00:53:18,880
<font color="yellow">How about 40 months then?</font>

957
00:53:18,880 --> 00:53:21,640
<font color="yellow">I can't believe you'd do this to us.</font>

958
00:53:39,900 --> 00:53:41,340
<font color="yellow">It's no joke.</font>

959
00:53:41,870 --> 00:53:44,000
<font color="yellow">You have great taste.</font>

960
00:53:44,670 --> 00:53:47,880
<font color="yellow">The artworks that you asked me to sell for you...</font>

961
00:53:47,880 --> 00:53:51,070
<font color="yellow">Some are worth 5,000 dollars and some even double that.</font>

962
00:53:54,100 --> 00:53:57,270
<font color="yellow">I guess you're destined to make a fortune.</font>

963
00:53:58,400 --> 00:54:01,200
<font color="yellow">I have neither a husband nor kids. I might as well have money.</font>

964
00:54:02,040 --> 00:54:04,500
<font color="yellow">Don't sell them. I just wanted to know their values.</font>

965
00:54:04,500 --> 00:54:06,990
<font color="yellow">What do you mean? Sell them all!</font>

966
00:54:06,990 --> 00:54:10,400
<font color="yellow">I just sent you the really nice ones.</font>

967
00:54:11,500 --> 00:54:14,370
<font color="yellow">Of course, they're worth more than what I paid for.</font>

968
00:54:14,370 --> 00:54:15,640
<font color="yellow">I'm Choong Nam.</font>

969
00:54:19,500 --> 00:54:23,940
<font color="yellow">They're the ignorant fools for not knowing how good they are.</font>

970
00:54:25,300 --> 00:54:28,270
<font color="yellow">They sold their masterpieces for a bargain price.</font>

971
00:54:29,600 --> 00:54:30,870
<font color="yellow">So what if they're professors?</font>

972
00:54:31,400 --> 00:54:33,770
<font color="yellow">Their brains and eyes are just for show.</font>

973
00:54:35,870 --> 00:54:37,070
<font color="yellow">This cafe's mine.</font>

974
00:54:37,570 --> 00:54:38,670
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

975
00:54:39,600 --> 00:54:40,870
<font color="yellow">Enjoy.</font>

976
00:54:42,200 --> 00:54:43,840
<font color="yellow">Isn't the weather lovely?</font>

977
00:54:46,140 --> 00:54:47,140
<font color="yellow">Why not...</font>

978
00:54:47,840 --> 00:54:49,640
<font color="yellow">get revenge?</font>

979
00:54:50,470 --> 00:54:52,500
<font color="yellow">If it would make their sad 60 or 70-year life...</font>

980
00:54:52,500 --> 00:54:55,140
<font color="yellow">worth living for even for a moment,</font>

981
00:54:56,500 --> 00:55:00,540
<font color="yellow">and if that were to make up for all the hardships they put up with...</font>

982
00:55:01,270 --> 00:55:02,500
<font color="yellow">If it comforts them,</font>

983
00:55:03,300 --> 00:55:05,870
<font color="yellow">then doesn't that make it all worthwhile?</font>

984
00:55:07,000 --> 00:55:08,440
<font color="yellow">They will die soon.</font>

985
00:55:09,000 --> 00:55:10,570
<font color="yellow">Their time is coming.</font>

986
00:55:11,100 --> 00:55:13,470
<font color="yellow">If we were to tell them...</font>

987
00:55:13,470 --> 00:55:15,900
<font color="yellow">to live their lives as they did so far,</font>

988
00:55:16,300 --> 00:55:17,900
<font color="yellow">wouldn't that be too cruel?</font>

989
00:55:18,700 --> 00:55:21,890
<font color="yellow">You forgot to write "I deserve to die."</font>

990
00:55:21,890 --> 00:55:22,900
<font color="yellow">Go on.</font>

991
00:55:23,570 --> 00:55:26,020
<font color="yellow">I'll have this carved on my tombstone.</font>

992
00:55:26,020 --> 00:55:28,570
<font color="yellow">So write it nicely and clearly.</font>

993
00:55:31,840 --> 00:55:34,700
<font color="yellow">(I am sorry.)</font>

994
00:55:46,140 --> 00:55:48,300
<font color="yellow">(I deserve to die.)</font>

995
00:55:55,600 --> 00:55:56,670
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

996
00:55:58,140 --> 00:55:59,140
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

997
00:56:06,350 --> 00:56:07,350
<font color="yellow">Mum?</font>

998
00:56:15,880 --> 00:56:16,880
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won.</font>

999
00:56:17,980 --> 00:56:19,880
<font color="yellow">Good evening.</font>

1000
00:56:19,880 --> 00:56:21,620
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

1001
00:56:23,720 --> 00:56:24,720
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

1002
00:56:31,220 --> 00:56:33,720
<font color="yellow">Did he send you those flowers?</font>

1003
00:56:34,880 --> 00:56:37,120
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- Meet up with him.</font>

1004
00:56:37,450 --> 00:56:39,680
<font color="yellow">You missed him. You should see him then.</font>

1005
00:56:41,880 --> 00:56:43,580
<font color="yellow">What if I'm disappointed?</font>

1006
00:56:44,680 --> 00:56:47,580
<font color="yellow">If you are, then call it quits.</font>

1007
00:56:49,450 --> 00:56:50,980
<font color="yellow">What does that make of my life?</font>

1008
00:56:53,250 --> 00:56:56,520
<font color="yellow">A life full of disappointments?</font>

1009
00:56:57,720 --> 00:56:59,480
<font color="yellow">My second marriage...</font>

1010
00:57:00,180 --> 00:57:03,350
<font color="yellow">was actually just me trying to get over him.</font>

1011
00:57:04,180 --> 00:57:06,120
<font color="yellow">But it didn't work.</font>

1012
00:57:10,880 --> 00:57:13,760
<font color="yellow">Is that why when you left him,</font>

1013
00:57:13,760 --> 00:57:16,620
<font color="yellow">you said it wasn't his fault?</font>

1014
00:57:16,620 --> 00:57:18,820
<font color="yellow">Because you weren't over Dae Cheol.</font>

1015
00:57:21,680 --> 00:57:25,250
<font color="yellow">If he hadn't gone back to his wife who drugged herself...</font>

1016
00:57:26,150 --> 00:57:29,580
<font color="yellow">because he married me, we'd still be together.</font>

1017
00:57:30,380 --> 00:57:33,520
<font color="yellow">I'm afraid I'll be disappointed in what he's become.</font>

1018
00:57:35,680 --> 00:57:38,720
<font color="yellow">But then again, I also miss him terribly.</font>

1019
00:57:41,680 --> 00:57:44,170
<font color="yellow">I'm so old now.</font>

1020
00:57:44,170 --> 00:57:45,550
<font color="yellow">I'm not as pretty either.</font>

1021
00:57:48,620 --> 00:57:49,850
<font color="yellow">Wan.</font>

1022
00:57:49,850 --> 00:57:52,750
<font color="yellow">Isn't it boring listening to an old lady talk about love?</font>

1023
00:57:55,220 --> 00:57:57,250
<font color="yellow">I think you're just beautiful.</font>

1024
00:57:59,150 --> 00:58:00,440
<font color="yellow">Should I go see him?</font>

1025
00:58:00,440 --> 00:58:02,550
<font color="yellow">Yes. I'm all for it.</font>

1026
00:58:08,050 --> 00:58:09,050
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won.</font>

1027
00:58:11,680 --> 00:58:14,150
<font color="yellow">I'm seeing Yeon Ha again.</font>

1028
00:58:15,820 --> 00:58:18,280
<font color="yellow">I went to go see him last week.</font>

1029
00:58:25,080 --> 00:58:28,450
<font color="yellow">I'm going to go. I have a night shoot.</font>

1030
00:58:28,450 --> 00:58:31,620
<font color="yellow">Okay. When I finish writing the book,</font>

1031
00:58:32,020 --> 00:58:34,820
<font color="yellow">I'm going back to Slovenia even if Mum disagrees.</font>

1032
00:58:36,250 --> 00:58:37,350
<font color="yellow">Call me.</font>

1033
00:58:39,280 --> 00:58:41,480
<font color="yellow">Okay. Bye.</font>

1034
00:58:54,680 --> 00:58:55,680
<font color="yellow">Lips.</font>

1035
00:59:01,020 --> 00:59:03,480
<font color="yellow">I'm suddenly so dizzy.</font>

1036
00:59:04,520 --> 00:59:06,020
<font color="yellow">What is it? Do you have a headache?</font>

1037
00:59:06,350 --> 00:59:07,350
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

1038
00:59:07,920 --> 00:59:11,060
<font color="yellow">I miss you so much that I don't want to see you.</font>

1039
00:59:11,060 --> 00:59:14,420
<font color="yellow">I miss you more now that I see you.</font>

1040
00:59:14,980 --> 00:59:16,180
<font color="yellow">It's so annoying.</font>

1041
00:59:21,520 --> 00:59:22,620
<font color="yellow">It's not funny.</font>

1042
00:59:23,580 --> 00:59:24,650
<font color="yellow">It's hard for me.</font>

1043
00:59:26,920 --> 00:59:30,280
<font color="yellow">I went to church today.</font>

1044
00:59:30,680 --> 00:59:32,550
<font color="yellow">This is where you and I...</font>

1045
00:59:33,380 --> 00:59:35,850
<font color="yellow">Don't put it down. I want to see it for longer.</font>

1046
00:59:49,580 --> 00:59:52,680
<font color="yellow">It would be so nice to get married there.</font>

1047
01:00:22,680 --> 01:00:23,850
<font color="yellow">(Passbook)</font>

1048
01:00:26,920 --> 01:00:29,080
<font color="yellow">Do you want a drink since we got our pay?</font>

1049
01:00:31,450 --> 01:00:32,550
<font color="yellow">No drinks?</font>

1050
01:00:33,420 --> 01:00:36,250
<font color="yellow">I'll just get beer with my wife then.</font>

1051
01:00:37,180 --> 01:00:38,180
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

1052
01:00:47,620 --> 01:00:49,750
<font color="yellow">I left you some food at home.</font>

1053
01:00:49,750 --> 01:00:51,020
<font color="yellow">I'll come visit in two days.</font>

1054
01:00:54,350 --> 01:00:56,380
<font color="yellow">(Summer vacation's special promotion)</font>

1055
01:00:56,380 --> 01:01:00,280
<font color="yellow">When are you going to quit? When can we go on our trip?</font>

1056
01:01:00,750 --> 01:01:04,610
<font color="yellow">You'll really go this time when you retire from security, right?</font>

1057
01:01:04,610 --> 01:01:07,360
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to finish your sentence for you?</font>

1058
01:01:07,360 --> 01:01:09,420
<font color="yellow">You know I've been patient with you.</font>

1059
01:01:09,420 --> 01:01:12,280
<font color="yellow">I took care of your parents until they were in diapers.</font>

1060
01:01:12,280 --> 01:01:14,880
<font color="yellow">I raised and fed your eight siblings,</font>

1061
01:01:14,880 --> 01:01:16,850
<font color="yellow">and married them off.</font>

1062
01:01:17,680 --> 01:01:19,820
