1077
01:02:28,650 --> 01:02:29,780
<font color="yellow">(Osaka and Okinawa)</font>

1078
01:02:42,820 --> 01:02:44,620
<font color="yellow">Are you happy now?</font>

1079
01:02:44,620 --> 01:02:46,350
<font color="yellow">You won and I lost.</font>

1080
01:02:46,350 --> 01:02:49,100
