<font color="yellow">She's evil.</font>

1102
01:04:45,850 --> 01:04:49,980
<font color="yellow">She trained me so that I can't do anything without her.</font>

1103
01:04:51,150 --> 01:04:54,980
<font color="yellow">She acted as if she would do everything for me like my mum.</font>

1104
01:04:57,620 --> 01:04:59,720
<font color="yellow">I... I didn't...</font>

1105
01:05:00,450 --> 01:05:02,920
<font color="yellow">just ask her to come back home.</font>

1106
01:05:03,980 --> 01:05:05,020
